    {
      "id": "0683a539-4ac5-4c55-a2b3-811ca553bba0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "LMS are a limited option to evaluate student performance and the authors propose a new model that not only uses LMS data but uses Internet usage patterns as well. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "0683a539-4ac5-4c55-a2b3-811ca553bba0",
        "parent": {
